replies.body:
This definitely sounds like LoL's connection to you is getting blocked or interrupted by something now and then; that's the primary cause for freezes and Champ Select issues, and even black screens. ;_;

No worries though, we have a guide that can eliminate any potential causes for Connection. Run through [**the steps listed here**](http://riot.com/12B7oac) to clear up any blockages for League. Your champ select should be plagued no longer by connection related problems then, but if you still get those freezes and black screens don't hesitate to hit me up again so I can look for another fix!

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
